title: Thursday Pt1: Carson Wentz vs. Justin Fields; Cowboys-Eagles trivia; Can Jets upset Packers in Lambeau?
itunes:title: Thursday Pt1: Carson Wentz vs. Justin Fields; Cowboys-Eagles trivia; Can Jets upset Packers in Lambeau?
description:
Part One of the Good Morning Football Podcast begins with hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Super Bowl Champion Jason McCourty looking into the ups and downs of Carson Wentz’s career and then Peter leads mixed bag trivia with a Dallas Cowboys-Philadelphia Eagles theme in honor of Sunday Night Football. Part one of the GMFB podcast finishes up discussing if the New York Jets can go into Lambeau and upset the Green Bay Packers?

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
